snippet: Robin Williams’s autopsy found no alcohol or illegal drugs were in his body when he killed himself at his Northern California home on Aug. 11, Marin County sheriff’s officials said Friday.
abstract: Autopsy of actor Robin Williams's body finds no traces of alcohol or illegal drugs in his system when he committed suicide at his Northern California home in August.
lead_paragraph: Robin Williams’s autopsy found no alcohol or illegal drugs were in his body when he killed himself at his Northern California home on Aug. 11, Marin County sheriff’s officials said Friday.

headline.main: California: Robin Williams’s Autopsy Shows No Illicit Drugs
headline.print_headline: California: Actor’s Autopsy Shows No Illicit Drugs
